Chris Kattan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Kattan 0 Christopher Lee Kattan (; born October 19, 1970) is an American actor and comedian, best known for his work as a cast member on Saturday Night Live, his role as Bob on the first four seasons of The Middle, for playing Doug Butabi in A Night at the Roxbury and Bunnicula in Bunnicula.
